This IS season 5.  There is a pretty exhaustive list of episodes for USA seaons on Wikipedia ( http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Family_Guy_episodes ) and you can plainly see that season 5 is listed as such.  If in the UK or any country other than the USA, you will find that the seasons are different.  For instance, here in the UK there is a Season SIX DVD set that is in fact, Season FIVE as listed on this torrent.  This is because Season Three got split in two and mixed around.
